   Firebase: disabled -- set FIREBASE_CREDENTIALS and FIREBASE_DATABASE_URL
Routes:
  POST /upload         upload blueprint image
  GET  /is-free        check robot placement validity
  POST /set-pose       set robot start position (validated)
  POST /navigate       navigate to a room
  GET  /status         get system status
  GET  /get-command    ESP32 polls for next command
  POST /command-done   ESP32 confirms command executed
  GET  /grid.png       grid overlay (raw walls dark red + inflated yellow)
  GET  /path.png       path overlay
  GET  /debug_grid.png debug grid
  POST /manual-move    d-pad manual movement
 * Serving Flask app 'app'
 * Debug mode: on
